{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351869687,"sessionID":"ses_31c036d66ffeb3gOzUVP7hTP5i","part":{"id":"prt_ce40195da001EjzdQPT77s69Ml","sessionID":"ses_31c036d66ffeb3gOzUVP7hTP5i","messageID":"msg_ce4018b410012JSSRW6YXZbvPn","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nRetrofit `--output json` support across all CLI commands in the `wombo` project. The JSON output was previously only implemented for some `features` subcommands (list, show, add, set-status, graph). The task is to add it to the remaining `features` subcommands (check, archive) and all operational commands (status, launch, upgrade, cleanup, verify, merge, resume, retry).\n\n## Instructions\n\n- **Branch:** `feature/json-output-complete` (already checked out)\n- **Commit guidelines:** Use conventional commits with scope `json-output-complete`, commit after each logical unit of work, do NOT squash, do NOT push to remote, do NOT modify `.features.yml`\n- **Constraint:** Human-friendly text output must remain the default\n- **Constraint:** JSON schemas should be consistent with existing features subcommand patterns\n- **Subtask order:** (1) features check, (2) features archive, (3) all operational commands\n- **Build verification:** Run `bun run build` after all changes and fix any errors before considering complete\n- The output utility module at `src/lib/output.ts` provides `output()`, `outputError()`, `outputMessage()`, `resolveOutputFormat()`, and `filterFields*` helpers — all commands should use these\n- The `OutputFormat` type is `\"text\" | \"json\"` — commands receive it via their options interface as `outputFmt?: OutputFormat`\n- `index.ts` parses `--output` / `-o` flags and passes `outputFmt` to command handlers\n\n## Discoveries\n\n- The existing pattern for JSON-retrofitted commands: accept `outputFmt?: OutputFormat` in options, resolve with `const fmt = opts.outputFmt ?? \"text\"`, use `output(fmt, data, textRenderer)` for final output, `outputError(fmt, msg)` for errors, `outputMessage(fmt, msg, extra)` for simple messages\n- For interactive/long-running commands (launch monitoring loop, resume monitoring loop), JSON output only makes sense for the initial response (dry-run, error exits). The live TUI/monitoring parts remain text-only — guarded with `if (fmt !== \"json\")` checks\n- The `outputError` function calls `process.exit(1)` — it's typed as `never`, so existing `process.exit(1)` calls should be replaced with it\n- `mergeBranch` returns `{success, commitHash: string | null, error: string | null}` — need `?? undefined` when assigning to optional typed fields to avoid TS null/undefined mismatch\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed:\n1. **features check** — Retrofitted with `{ok, issues, errors, warnings, items_checked}` JSON schema. File written and index.ts updated.\n2. **features archive** — Retrofitted with `{archived: [{id, title, status}], count}` JSON schema. File written and index.ts updated.\n3. **First commit made** — `feat(json-output-complete): retrofit features check and archive with --output json`\n4. **status.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output support (`{wave_id, base_branch, counts, agents}`)\n5. **launch.ts** — `LaunchCommandOptions` updated with `outputFmt`, `cmdLaunch` updated for dry-run JSON output and error paths. Import for `output, outputError` added.\n6. **cleanup.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output for both dry-run and execution paths\n7. **verify.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output (`{wave_id, verified, count}`)\n8. **merge.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output (`{wave_id, merged, count, pushed}`), fixed TS null/undefined issues\n9. **resume.ts** — Options interface updated with `outputFmt`, error path at start uses `outputError`\n10. **retry.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output for all paths (dry-run, errors, success)\n11. **upgrade.ts** — Fully rewritten with JSON output for all paths (check, install, up-to-date, errors)\n\n### In Progress:\n- **index.ts updates** — `upgrade` call updated to pass `outputFmt`. Still need to update: `launch`, `resume`, `status`, `verify`, `merge`, `retry`, `cleanup` calls in the switch statement to pass `args.outputFmt`\n\n### Remaining:\n1. Finish updating all command invocations in `index.ts` switch statement to pass `outputFmt`\n2. Fix the `retry` error handling in index.ts (currently uses `console.error` + `process.exit(1)` before calling `cmdRetry` — should use outputFmt-aware error)\n3. Run `bun run build` to verify everything compiles\n4. Fix any build errors\n5. Commit the operational commands changes\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n- `src/lib/output.ts` — Output utility module (read, not modified) — provides `output()`, `outputError()`, `outputMessage()`, `filterFields()`, `OutputFormat`\n- `src/lib/state.ts` — Wave/Agent state types (read, not modified) — `WaveState`, `AgentState`, `agentCounts()`\n- `src/lib/ui.ts` — Dashboard rendering (read, not modified) — `printDashboard()`, `printAgentUpdate()`\n- `src/index.ts` — CLI entry point (partially modified) — needs remaining command invocations updated to pass `outputFmt`\n- `src/commands/features/check.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/features/archive.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/status.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/launch.ts` — ✅ Partially retrofitted (options + cmdLaunch entry, internal monitoring loops intentionally text-only)\n- `src/commands/cleanup.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/verify.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/merge.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/resume.ts` — Partially retrofitted (options + initial error, rest of function not modified)\n- `src/commands/retry.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- `src/commands/upgrade.ts` — ✅ Fully retrofitted\n- Already-retrofitted reference files (read for pattern reference): `src/commands/features/list.ts`, `src/commands/features/show.ts`, `src/commands/features/add.ts`, `src/commands/features/set-status.ts`","time":{"start":1773351869686,"end":1773351869686}}}
